		<title>Ebook Marketing Strategies for 2015 — What Will Work?</title>
		<link>http://www.lindsayburoker.com/e-publishing/ebook-marketing-strategies-for-2015-what-will-work/</link>
		<comments>http://www.lindsayburoker.com/e-publishing/ebook-marketing-strategies-for-2015-what-will-work/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Mon, 05 Jan 2015 19:54:36 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Lindsay]]></dc:creator>
