<li><a href="http://www.lindsayburoker.com/news/summer-projects-and-will-there-be-more-emperors-edge-after-republic/" title="Summer Projects and Will There Be More &#8220;Emperor&#8217;s Edge&#8221; After Republic?">Summer Projects and Will There Be More &#8220;Emperor&#8217;s Edge&#8221; After Republic?</a></li>
</ul>
<div class="shr-publisher-4937"></div><!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic --><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><div class='shareaholic-like-buttonset' style='float:none;height:30px;'><a class='shareaholic-googleplusone' data-shr_size='medium' data-shr_count='true' data-shr_href='http://www.lindsayburoker.com/ebook-news/dragon-blood-book-4/' data-shr_title='Patterns+in+the+Dark+%28Dragon+Blood+Book+4%29+Available+Everywhere'></a><a class='shareaholic-tweetbutton' data-shr_count='horizontal' data-shr_href='http://www.lindsayburoker.com/ebook-news/dragon-blood-book-4/' data-shr_title='Patterns+in+the+Dark+%28Dragon+Blood+Book+4%29+Available+Everywhere'></a><a class='shareaholic-fblike' data-shr_layout='button_count' data-shr_showfaces='false' data-shr_href='http://www.lindsayburoker.com/ebook-news/dragon-blood-book-4/' data-shr_title='Patterns+in+the+Dark+%28Dragon+Blood+Book+4%29+Available+Everywhere'></a><a class='shareaholic-fbsend' data-shr_href='http://www.lindsayburoker.com/ebook-news/dragon-blood-book-4/'></a></div><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic --><!-- Start Shareaholic Recommendations Automatic --><!-- End Shareaholic Recommendations Automatic --><div class="feedflare">
